in the mean time we will collect evidence of their crime

244
00:16:38,300 --> 00:16:40,840
we also have handled Yuguo situation

245
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:43,780
so there is no one else that know we are still alive

246
00:16:43,780 --> 00:16:46,530
even though the situation happened we still don't have physical evidence

247
00:16:46,530 --> 00:16:48,160
