248
00:16:48,160 --> 00:16:49,890
make sure you don't get caught

249
00:16:49,890 --> 00:16:51,580
Anxin and I will live here

250
00:16:51,580 --> 00:16:54,180
I already discussed with my elder brother, he will keep the secret

251
00:16:54,180 --> 00:16:57,440
and spread news that we are dead

252
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:59,130
